{"tid":1248818,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓高音喇叭廣播反覆向北韓撥放脫北士兵的新聞","createTime":"2019-06-21T14:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T07:15:34.000Z","uid":84849,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a38dc04d0ceedd36831cd38f5504af26aece9909","tid":1248818,"uid":84849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:26:25.000Z","msg":"高音喇叭廣播什麼呢？它其實攸關 南韓對北韓的統獨心理戰 。<br />\n<br />\n從 1963 年開始，南韓軍方在北韓邊境附近設置了十幾處廣播設施，每一處安裝著 48 個高音喇叭，向邊境地區的北韓軍人廣播。南韓的國防部曾經說過，這些廣播夜間甚至可以傳 20 公里遠。<br />\n<br />\n而這些高音喇叭都在喧鬧些什麼呢？多半 是南韓的最新新聞、天氣預報、最新韓劇（廣播劇）、K-pop 歌曲，甚至直接批評北韓總統金正恩的內容，另外，高音喇叭也曾反覆向北韓撥放脫北士兵的新聞 ，予以挑釁。<br />\n<br />\n咁啲士兵守住又無得岀去咪會精神崩潰 最後倒戈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd650d6de4ec1470776d09a329c7d7d4c422b3a3","tid":1248818,"uid":84849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa93a8d2c937c3480078dd08336f32937f1a469","tid":1248818,"uid":84849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:30:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769c5a43bf190777348f284e6aa2573f8de06942","tid":1248818,"uid":84849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:32:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e8fc1116e17d56e97322bd40556348ea1de150d","tid":1248818,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:32:17.000Z","msg":"可以係咁播D youtube屌黑警既片"},{"pid":"9e5bcc98b8cb95bf4b05d689faf704a3b529e621","tid":1248818,"uid":166245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e8fc1116e17d56e97322bd40556348ea1de150d","tid":1248818,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:32:17.000Z","msg":"可以係咁播D youtube屌黑警既片"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:33:54.000Z","msg":"播一哥割席嘅新聞<img src=\"/asset